messages.content:
Hello , 

Due to unforeseen demand , we are not able to address each request so we have decided to digitise all lakes around hyderabad and make it accessible for free 

To help prioritise the digitisation process, fill the following form with your requirements. We will inform you once your required lake is digitised. 
Requirement form : https://forms.gle/LFThdXChRzH8Uz6M6 

Thanks for your patience.
